#. type: multicols
#: sections/combat.tex:14
msgid "Combat with \\textbf{another player} can start in two ways:"
msgstr ""
"Walkę z \\textbf{drugim Graczem} można rozpocząć na dwa sposoby:"

#. type: itemize
#: sections/combat.tex:14
